  "title": "fix(hitsPerPage): avoid sync default value",
  "body": "This PR avoid to sync the default value into the `uiState`. This behavior is consistent with the one from `sortBy`. The default value doesn't have to be inside the `uiState` because as the name suggests it's the default one. The option is defined statically, it can't change.",
